{"tid":1478751,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工做過啲咩尷尬野？","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T00:09:35.000Z","uid":57308,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87482aebe45abb7bf0259eba730eda7108687c7b","tid":1478751,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"有次趁啲師父放飯，趁冇安全佬，咪落地盤睇進度<br />\n嗰日朝早飲左杯凍豆漿，成個上午個肚都咕嚕咕嚕咁叫，痾完都成肚氣<br />\n見地盤冇人<br />\n咪偷偷地放鬆個菊花放咁啲氣<br />\n聽到啲聲真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺個咁空曠既地方盡情放響屁你都咪話唔爽<br />\n一次過爆發晒出嚟既感覺真係仲正過&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知一轉個角見到有個師父鋪左啲紙皮落地下瞓<br />\n佢眼甘甘咁望住我<br />\n仆你個街陰鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩之後其他盤都唔見嗰個師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff563565510861298a35ae1da212886e706e895","tid":1478751,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92232ded726bee3c8754992ef6884357665c9529","tid":1478751,"uid":73244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"做地盤佬放個屁都斯斯縮縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪玩啦ching"},{"pid":"c77ed6457f2a91685b48be98ddcf6cea82c0ad77",